snippet.title: Dragon Ball FighterZ - PS4/XB1/PC/SWITCH - Cooler (EVO Trailer)
snippet.description:
We are delighted to announce that the release date of the original version of Goku and Vegeta DLC for Dragon Ball FighterZ is set to August 8th.
But this trailer has much more to say: welcome Cooler as the next Dragon Ball FighterZ's DLC!
